'''Trnsko''' is a neighbourhood of [[Zagreb]], [[Croatia]], located south of [[Dubrovnik Avenue]] in [[Novi Zagreb - zapad]]. The population is 5,331 (2011).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.zagreb.hr/default.aspx?id=15059|title=16. Mjesni odbor Trnsko|accessdate=10 January 2015}}</ref>

Trnsko was one of [[Novi Zagreb]]'s first neighbourhoods constructed in early 1960s. The streets have no names, but the orientation is easy - Trnsko 1 is on the north and Trnsko 49 on the far south of the neighbourhood.

